about.name: Haingo Razafindranto
about.title: About me
about.description: Hello, I'm Haingo, an IT enthusiast who graduated in July 2023. My journey in the tech world began even before graduation as I delved into part-time work experiences starting in August 2022. These early ventures provided me with invaluable real-world exposure and practical skills, shaping my understanding of the industry. Now, equipped with a solid foundation from my academic pursuits, I'm looking forward to furthering my studies while continuing to explore and contribute to the dynamic field of technology. Within this portfolio, you'll find a selection of projects that showcase my passion, skills, and dedication.
